{"tid":2361019,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"四口家三人冇工開「好似天跌落嚟」","createTime":"2021-01-10T09:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T10:36:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb821bacc6e3bcb0692987748e280e41c484bcac","tid":2361019,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T09:55:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/JXXSVNVTX5CF3MUKN2ZLATBQZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FJXXSVNVTX5CF3MUKN2ZLATBQZE%2F&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7aEelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=635bbc46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FJXXSVNVTX5CF3MUKN2ZLATBQZE%2F&h=d5cb80f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/JXXSVNVTX5CF3MUKN2ZLATBQZE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n四口家三人冇工開「好似天跌落嚟」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Bz7fUAtx9A5vFd_jgZ-T2LG_q-E=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TKM6VZALXVDIZLC4ZGOVZT6WHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBz7fUAtx9A5vFd_jgZ-T2LG_q-E%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTKM6VZALXVDIZLC4ZGOVZT6WHE.jpg&h=192035ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■一家四口有三人失業，May形容如天塌下來。<br />\n<br />\nMay一家四口居於面積100多呎的劏房，屬低收入家庭，平日需向社福機構領取食物援助。一場疫症，令除了在學的幼子外，其餘三人也成為失業人口，把他們推入谷底。<br />\n<br />\n最早失業是大學畢業近一年多的長女Kennie（化名），修讀環境工程的Kennie去年大學畢業，在私人公司找到相關職位的全職工作，但去年3月合約期滿後，公司就不再續約，至今仍未找到工作。<br />\n<br />\n第二位失業的是May的丈夫，從事地盤散工的丈夫收入勉強餬口，但適逢疫情工作量減少，近兩個月收入變得不穩。加上多個地盤爆疫，丈夫亦加入失業大軍。<br />\n<br />\n噩夢接踵而來，從事幼稚園清。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YerKX3bvbezO86TuueZepdb-dh0=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PUC5ALZNCNBDPBH5FLBJVMWPS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYerKX3bvbezO86TuueZepdb-dh0%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPUC5ALZNCNBDPBH5FLBJVMWPS4.jpg&h=837219d9&s={SIZE}\" />                               <br />\n■Kennie暫時在社會機構任兼職，她希望能找到文職工作。林幸泉攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行行失業 散工都要搶<br />\n<br />\n失業九個月的Kennie心情複雜，她未有預計會面對此困境，意志日復日被消磨，Kennie求職門檻亦降至只要文職就可，「我𠵱家肯定係無所謂，文職就可以，降低要求，唔可以再執着於自己嗰科」。<br />\n<br />\n協助May的關注綜援低收入。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n統計處數字顯示，去年9至11月，25歲以下失業人口高達415,000人，佔整體失業人口35.3%，較去年同期的264,000人增加57%。<br />\n<br />\n李大成甚至收過前國泰機師的求職信，認為市場「搶工」問題嚴重，「青年畢業之後都係做散工，但𠵱家散工都『抆抆地』，旅遊、航空、零售失業，四圍搶」。他促請現政府增加職位，協助年輕人就業。"},{"pid":"53443da6724df8a915ba786fa8ea74fc666535d8","tid":2361019,"uid":46737,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T09:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做工程未見過有停工"},{"pid":"fd9734e4ce23e8f9cc1e1077880e86b6d8c089f1","tid":2361019,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:06:30.000Z","msg":"綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3844374e4d6f9fb8a22a983eabb1f10052c12d6b","tid":2361019,"uid":58385,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:36:56.000Z","msg":"環境工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到好委屈咁要簡文職，佢知唔知大把有十年廿年既人爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npart time完做下外賣仔+增值自己好過啦"}]}